= [[Mac OS X]] =

To show existing ACLs on an entity, e.g `foo`:

<pre lang="shell">$ ls -le foo</pre>

To add an item to the ACL for `foo`:

<pre lang="shell">$ chmod +a 'username:allow read,write' foo</pre>

For a full list of possible perimissions, see [http://developer.apple.com/library/mac/#documentation/Darwin/Reference/ManPages/man1/chmod.1.html the Mac OS X chmod man page].

For a concerete example of setting up ACLs on Mac OS X, see "[[Installing nginx 0.8.54 on Mac OS X 10.6.6 Snow Leopard]]".

